Window

Class Container

  • java.lang.Object
    • Support.mvc.TController
      • Support.navigator.TNavigator
        • Window.Container
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyChangeListener, EventListener, IController, INavigator, IContainer

    public class Container
extends TNavigator
implements IContainer
    Contains the implementation of application controller component specified by IContainer interface. The class extends the TNavigator general purpose abstract navigator class.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Sandor Kalmanchey
